{
  "stem": "10818.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So meanwhile, he started building up a livelihood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because of the war, actually, things got better in this country economically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was able to be a salesman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was very respected as a sales-- he was very diligent and correct and you know, started making a fairly good living, I mean, So that he could go to an auction.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we came here with nothing, with no-- not a stick of furniture, literally the clothes on our back, backs and what we had in the suitcases.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we moved out of this boarding house to an apartment in-- a small apartment in Forest Hills, which-- during the war, things were rather fluid, and you could find an apartment, because people moved to Washington-- I remember the people that we sublet from at first moved to Washington.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they left a sofa and maybe a couple of old beds there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother, she got around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know when people die, sometimes a whole household sort of gets sold for practically nothing?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, for $25, she picked up a bunch of household goods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, it was a lot to spend $25.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she-- she furnished us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I slept on that sleep sofa in the living room until I got married.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we still had it, and we still got it, I guess, even into this house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, for years and years and years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day-- and we used it as a, as a guest bedroom.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, my father said, I'm not going to come here anymore if I have to sleep on that sofa.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was so rotten.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And fortunately by that time, we were able to buy a new sofa.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
